full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/13/2023 Attachment to Form I-692 Page Two A91 318 117 On June 2, 1988 you were requested to provide additional documentation concerning your medical. A copy of that request is attached and made part of this order You have failed to submit the required documentation to support your application. Therefore, the evidence submitted is insufficient to support your claim and your application is hereby denied.
